1. Naša soba je uvek u *haosu* kad se vratimo s puta. (Our room is always in *chaos* when we come back from a trip.)
2. Njihova veza je u potpunom *haosu*. (Their relationship is in complete *chaos*.)
3. Ukoliko ne uredimo *haos* u kancelariji, nećemo biti efikasni. (If we don't tidy up the *chaos* in the office, we won't be efficient.)
4. Vozila su se sudarila i napravila veliki *haos* na putu. (The vehicles crashed and caused a big *mess* on the road.)
5. Njegov život se pretvorio u *haos* nakon što je izgubio posao. (His life turned into *chaos* after he lost his job.)
6. Nemoj mi praviti *haos* svojim nepotrebnim komentarima. (Don't create *trouble* with your unnecessary comments.)
7. Naš plan se pretvorio u potpuni *haos* nakon što smo se izgubili. (Our plan turned into complete *disarray* after we got lost.)
8. Iako izgleda kao *haos*, oni imaju svoj sistem rada. (Although it looks like *chaos*, they have their own system of work.)
9. Naša zemlja se suočava sa *haosom* u političkoj situaciji. (Our country is facing *turmoil* in the political situation.)
10. Prošle noći je bilo *haotično* u klubu. (It was *chaotic* in the club last night.)